      <div xml:id="NA383-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu tōḻi āṟupārttuṟṟuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what is said to the confidante after the experience of looking at the path.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA383">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            kallayaṟ kalitta karuṅkāl vēṅkai</l>
<l>            yalaṅkalan toṭalai yaṉṉa kuruḷai</l>
<l>            vayappuṉiṟ ṟirumpiṇāp pacitteṉa vayappuli</l>
<l>            pukarmukañ citaiyat tākkik kaḷiṟaṭ</l>
<l>            ṭurumicai yuraṟu muṭkuvaru naṭunā</l>
<l>            ḷaruḷiṉai pōliṉu marulā yaṉṟē</l>
<l>            kaṉaiyiruḷ putaitta vañcuvaru miyaviṟ</l>
<l>            pāmpuṭaṉ ṟirikku murumō</l>
<l>            ṭōṅkuvarai nāṭanī varuta lāṉē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent4">          At dreadful midnight,</l>
<l rend="indent">          when the strong tiger roars with the voice of thunder, having</l>
<l rend="indent">         killed the elephant bull, attacking so that [its] spotted face was spoiled,</l>
<l rend="indent2">         since the dark female [tiger] was hungry,</l>
<l rend="indent2">         with [its] strong newborn one,<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">puṉiṟṟu</term>: T.V.G. prefers to read this as a further attribute to <term xml:lang="ta">piṇā</term>.</note></l>
<l rend="indent3">         the young one like a swaying pretty garland</l>
<l rend="indent3">         of the black-trunked kino tree grown near the stones,</l>
<l>       even if it seems you [are] considerate, you are not considerate, no<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">aruḷāy aṉṟu</term>: actually it seems as if we have one negation too many here, so it seems best to take it as an apposition: "you are not, it is not".</note>,</l>
<l rend="indent">         because of your coming, o man from a land of high mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent2">         with the thunder that furiously drives away the snakes,</l>
<l rend="indent3">         on a fearful way buried in intense darkness.</l>
       </lg>
      </div>
